sentence: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the SPDR S&P 1500 Value Tilt ETF (Symbol: VLU) shows an impressive 10.1% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.

Citigroup Inc (Symbol: C), which makes up 1.21% of the SPDR S&P 1500 Value Tilt ETF (Symbol: VLU), has seen 4 directors and officers purchase shares in the past six months, according to the recent Form 4 data.
The ETF holds a total of $47,606 worth of C, making it the #12 largest holding.
